發現有一支友軍由頭到尾支持拜登, 你會開心定走去批鬥佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聰明既連登仔相信已經知道答案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算拜登唔想幫香港我地都要焗佢幫, 回想上年侵係唔多想理香港, 佢只想搞好連任, 係陰錯陽差搞到佢要提前收拾老共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 我十分感謝侵對香港既恩情, 但亦唔會忘記對中國既制裁係共和黨+民主黨合力促成<br />\n<br />\n另外, 已經有大量五毛代表香港人或台灣人係facebook or twitter四出批鬥民主黨or拜登or支持拜登既人, 有D國際線既手足無端端比人鬧, 大家見到幫下手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問: 咁樓主既立場係咩?<br />\n答: 我十分感謝侵對香港既恩情, 亦十分感謝共和黨+民主黨對香港既支持, 我相信拜登可以處理好中共<br />\n問: 你又支持侵又支持拜登, 想點ar?<br />\n答: 拜登贏左梗係同佢搞好關係, 有乜問題? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問: 牆頭草, 咁無恥咯你<br />\n答: 無計, 隔離有個流氓大國, 我係佢地到學既<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Be Water, 各位手足</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/newsweek/status/1320735256220176392?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewsweek%2Fstatus%2F1320735256220176392%3Fs%3D21&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=fdf5a051\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewsweek%2Fstatus%2F1320735256220176392%3Fs%3D21&h=7e346149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/newsweek/status/1320735256220176392?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n中共慣用手段"},{"pid":"e85b17cd499e854fdd3f9dd584a630823002779e","tid":2275794,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ed90206c38eb5a1e1c39796c26b1c23b5035256","tid":2275794,"uid":204539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:19:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">1. 扮成狂熱既侵粉批鬥民主黨+拜登</span><br />\n<br />\n好多連登仔唔係扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係真心<br />\n咁係咪五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"john weak個堆我都唔覺佢地係五毛