<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問: 咁樓主既立場係咩?<br />\n答: 我十分感謝侵對香港既恩情, 亦十分感謝共和黨+民主黨對香港既支持, 我相信拜登可以處理好中共<br />\n問: 你又支持侵又支持拜登, 想點ar?<br />\n答: 拜登贏左梗係同佢搞好關係, 有乜問題? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問: 牆頭草, 咁無恥咯你<br />\n答: 無計, 隔離有個流氓大國, 我係佢地到學既<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Be Water, 各位手足</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"好耐之前見到有個類似po但係講當時五毛分演極端和極端勇 從中分化和勇<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"其實來來去去都係果幾招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8007eb60edbf1f766548ec9974228b958b8e428","tid":2275794,"uid":318300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14143290a0e9ac4af75e299e4151c14f9ac5394b","tid":2275794,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"上面個濟癲學術台開埋啲廢post, 分明係類似高登洪非凡套路啲五毛黎<br />\n全部post都係同佢吹出黎hku讀哲學, 但講啲野廢過梁天琦九萬倍<br />\n唔覺得hku philo會出個垃圾覆野覆一兩句, 求其quote啲書名出黎當答左人, 完全講唔到對內容有咩見解<br />\n擺明有意做個假身份出黎分化連登"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"其實我都發現自己blk左佢, 不過話定推post順便答下人, 話唔定佢係個好人呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd39a0bfbd921a8027f8cd6e6802b9164b642d0e","tid":2275794,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"推 CCTVB俾人杯葛咗成年唔順氣，尋晚終於要借住《愛&middot;回家》單單打打 #2 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/gncDqT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gncDqT</a>"},{"pid":"fe81f131c27ac599c9edb3340b87579166df7fc7","tid":2275794,"uid":318300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0621a7093a0b9af9467b6e51cf4f4b7e92fd933e","tid"